snippet.textDisplay: I freaking love his new look!! Excellent work Brad!! I honestly love watching videos of ppl reacting to stuff that deals with their professions. I love singing..so I got into voice teachers react..and I am interested in music production and have found at least one music producer reacts..I've seen special efx ppl react to movies and such.. like it is fascinating to me. Now I love Hyram and I am so glad I found his channel recently bc I've recently been uping my skincare routine game..so I love all the information I am learning. I feel youtube is saturated with Beauty guru's right now...but I was never big into makeup until the last 3 years when I started selling Senegence.. I started experimenting and getting creative and really loving doing my makeup for my videos and it gave me more content to do...but again I rarely wear makeup and I am way more interested in taking care of my skin and I think Hyram's channel is so refreshing bc there is not a lot of content out there on skincare...or maybe I just haven't searched enough. Anyway...this is like the perfect and best collaboration!! I loved both videos!
